  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this prospective, case series is to evaluate the surgical treatment of painful and
      disabling osteoarthrosis in the MTP-I joint by insertion of an Artelon MTP Spacer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
